  "2026-04-01T15:39:36.115Z",cursor-agent,"Implemented restore recovery for missing/deleted item files from history streams: restore now resolves history-only subjects when item file is absent, reconstructs current state from history for restore event diffs, and preserves lock + rollback behavior. Added unit coverage for missing-file and deleted-item recovery and integration coverage for strict policy failures and history-only restore. Verification: pnpm build passed; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/restore-command.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts passed."
